Opportunity Number for Crème is a module for Crème CRM 1.4.
It enables to replace the "reference" field when you view, create or edit the opportunities by an auto-increment unique integer field whose value can be user-chosen.

INSTALL:

1. You have to move the makina folder into the creme folder which contains all the others modules such as activesync, activites, ...

2. And finally (yes, that's all), you must add the module 'creme.opportunity_number' into the INSTALLED_CREME_APPS tuple in your settings file (local_setting.py)
